# Opening a Stripe Account in India
## Introduction to Stripe Support

To open a Stripe account in India, follow these steps:

* Enable JavaScript in your browser settings for the best experience on Stripe.
* Visit the Stripe website and navigate to the sign-up page.
* Fill out the registration form with your business and personal details.
* Verify your email address and phone number.
* Set up your business profile and banking information.
* Wait for Stripe to review and approve your account.

## Enabling JavaScript
You need JavaScript enabled in your browser settings for the best experience on Stripe. To do this:
1. Go to your browser settings.
2. Search for JavaScript settings.
3. Enable JavaScript.

